title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Great Britain - Buckingham Palace
description:
In this video we will fly over Buckingham Palace. Buckingham Palace is a London royal residence and the administrative headquarters of the monarch of the United Kingdom. Located in the City of Westminster, the palace is often at the centre of state occasions and royal hospitality. It has been a focal point for the British people at times of national rejoicing and mourning.
